{"lemma":"عَسْكَرِ","slug":"عَسْكَرِ","root":"ع.س.ك.ر","root_slug":"ع-س-ك-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-س-ك-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29110"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%92%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"army, soldiers"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to militarize"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to encamp"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Etymology tree\nProto-Indo-European *h₂lek-\nProto-Indo-European *-seti\nProto-Indo-European *h₂lékseti\nProto-Indo-Iranian *Hrákšati\nProto-Iranian *karah\nMiddle Persian lšklbor.?\nArabic عسكر\nProbably from Middle Persian lškl (/⁠laškar⁠/) with the -l-interpreted as the Arabic article ال (al-). Compare modern Persian لشکر (laškar). Alternatively and less likely, from Latin exercitus."},"ipa":["/ʕas.kar/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29110","headword_ar":"عَسْكَرٌ","root":"Eskr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", a Pers. word arabicized, (Ibn-El-Jawá- leekee, Mgh, Msb, K, *) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la$okarN","text_ar":"لَشْكَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An army:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasaAkiru","text_ar":"عَسَاكِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, O.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasokaru muqobilN","text_ar":"العَسْكَرُ مُقْبِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqobiluwna","text_ar":"مُقْبِلُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The army is coming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are coming."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A collection."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large number,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: (A, K:) as, of men, and of camels or other property, and of horses, and of dogs. (TA.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collectively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu laqaliylu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَقَلِيلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasokari","text_ar":"العَسْكَرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he has few beasts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TS, O, TA.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of night. (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasaAkiru","text_ar":"عَسَاكِرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alham~i","text_ar":"الهَمِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anxieties, coming one upon another, consecutively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEasokarN","text_ar":"مُعَسْكَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b8-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasokaraAni","text_ar":"العَسْكَرَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"'Arafeh and Minè"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earafapu waminFY","text_ar":"عَرَفَةُ وَمِنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (S, A, O, Msb, K:) because places of assembling. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","TA","S","A","O","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}